title: Café Relish ni Oide
original_name: カフェ Relish においで
sinopse:
Virtual reality? Nope, it's a café!

When the restaurant owned by Inui Yasamoto's big brother runs into financial difficulty, their ex-host regular Ookami comes up with the solution: an all-male version of a maid café!

(Source: DP Scanlations)
